  • Constructor Details

    • MenuItem

      public MenuItem​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String menuName, double price, int type)
      Creates a new MenuItem object.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the item.
      menuName - The text that will be displayed when the MenuItem is placed in a ListView.
      price - The price of the item.
      type - The type of the item. This is an int value from 1 to 4. 1 = Food, 2 = Coffee, 3 = Condiment, 4 = Other.
